      <div class="info-card"><div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="zap" size={22} /></div><strong>Physical Endurance</strong><p>Rhodiola enhances exercise performance by improving oxygen utilization and delaying fatigue onset. Studies show improved time-to-exhaustion and reduced perceived exertion during endurance exercise after rhodiola supplementation.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="shield" size={22} /></div><strong>Stress Resilience</strong><p>Rhodiola normalizes HPA axis function, preventing both cortisol excess (anxiety, weight gain) and cortisol depletion (burnout, chronic fatigue). This adaptogenic balance maintains appropriate stress response without overreaction.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="heart" size={22} /></div><strong>Mood Support</strong><p>MAO inhibition preserves serotonin and dopamine availability. A clinical trial found rhodiola comparable to sertraline for mild depression with significantly fewer side effects. Particularly effective when fatigue and low motivation accompany depressive symptoms.</p></div>
    </div>

